">Dalibor Rile</tspan></text><text fill="#383c44" font-family="Metropolis-Regular, Metropolis" font-size="12" letter-spacing="-.0221052635" opacity=".75"><tspan x="270" y="284">Works great, easy and fast, excellent design!</tspan></text><use fill="#000" filter="url(#d)" xlink:href="#c"/><use fill="#fff" fill-rule="evenodd" xlink:href="#c"/><text style="opacity:.6;font-family:Metropolis-Bold, Metropolis;font-size:14;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:-.0257894741;fill:#383c44"><tspan x="47.896421" y="183">Auke van der Meer</tspan></text><text fill="#383c44" font-family="Metropolis-Regular, Metropolis" font-size="12" letter-spacing="-.0221052635" opacity=".75"><tspan x="28" y="151">Just perfect.</tspan></text><use fill="#000" filter="url(#f)" xlink:href="#e"/><use fill="#fff" fill-rule="evenodd" xlink:href="#e"/><text style="opacity:.6;font-family:Metropolis-Bold, Metropolis;font-size:14;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:-.0257894741;fill:#383c44"><tspan x="446.167474" y="83">Majeed Zoabi</tspan></text><text fill="#383c44" font-family="Metropolis-Regular, Metropolis" font-size="12" letter-spacing="-.0221052635" opacity=".75"><tspan x="370" y="51">Sleek and professional!</tspan></text><use fill="#000" filter="url(#h)" xlink:href="#g"/><use fill="#fff" fill-rule="evenodd" xlink:href="#g"/><text fill="#383c44" font-family="Metropolis-Regular, Metropolis" font-size="12" letter-spacing="-.0221052635" opacity=".75"><tspan x="420" y="130">Natrium is easily the most robust and intuitive Nano </tspan><tspan x="420" y="150">wallet. It gives the most control over your wallet’s </tspan><tspan x="420" y="170">security, contacts, and representative choice. Sending </tspan><tspan x="420" y="190">and receiving couldn’t be easier. Highly recommended.</tspan></text><text style="opacity:.6;font-family:Metropolis-Bold, Metropolis;font-size:14;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:-.0257894741;fill:#383c44"><tspan x="667.846105" y="222">Nate Ryan</tspan></text><use fill="#000" filter="url(#j)" xlink